~ start
if ToolManager.has_farming_tools()
	Guide: [[Hi|Hello|Howdy]], nice to see you again.
	Guide: Is there anything I can help you with?
	- Ask about Farming
		Guide: You can till the ground with your hoe and then plant Corn & Tomatoes.
		Guide: You then need to water it once, and they each grow over 4 days.
	- Ask about Gathering
		Guide: You can chop down trees and mine rocks for extra resources.
		Guide: They are not currently used in this patch. More to come soon!
	- Ask about Animals
		Guide: You can feed the animals with the crates near their pastures.
		Guide: Feeding them will give you Milk & Eggs (and make them happy)
	- Ask about Combat
		Guide: To fight monsters like Goblins, use your axe tool the same way you would chop a tree.
		Guide: Or cast magic spells! Hotkeys can be found in Ask About Controls.
		Guide: Magic abilities like those currently have a cooldown, but later youll use mana on them.
		Guide: Keep your health above 0 by eating food and hit them enough times to kill them.
		Guide: Monsters can drop different loot depending on their type!
	- Ask about Controls
		Guide: Escape takes you to main menu. WASD for character movement.
		Guide: Tab swaps between Farming or Combat Tool Bars, Combat shows your cooldowns for moves.
		Guide: Left Mouse Click to select tools, or eat food in your inventory.
		Guide: Right Click with a tool will use it or attack with the axe in the direction you are facing.
		Guide: P will quick save. E will interact with chests, like this guide. 
		Guide: B will pull up your Inventory. Q will pull up your quest log.
		Guide: CTRL+Right Click with the hoe will clear a tilled soil patch / crop patch.
		Guide: Z will quick eat eggs for 15 health, X will quick eat milk for 20 health, if you have it.
		Guide: F casts Fire Nova, an area of effect attack around the player. G casts fireball, a ranged cast attack. 
		Guide: R casts Holy Nova, which heals you and deals a small amount of damage around the player.
	- Ask about Objectives
		Guide: You can farm crops and animal products to use as food.
		Guide: Take your food into battle to fight enemies with spells and melee!
		Guide: Get gold to purchase different farming seeds & various products
		Guide: Quests are another way to get rewards, talk to npcs to find if they have quests to give you!
else
	Guide: [[Hi|Hello|Howdy]], nice to meet you.
	Guide: Welcome to SarahDewValley!
	Guide: As you can see the cows and chickens are hungry.
	Guide: You need to grow some crops to feed them!
	Guide: Here are some seeds and tools to grow some crops.
	- Take crop seeds
		Player: Yeah I can grow crops!
		do GameDialogueManager.action_give_crop_seeds()
	- No, I don't want them
		Player: No, I'm not ready to grow my farm yet.
=> END